{"tid":1729444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"怎麼才算出力攻入Poly/CU?","createTime":"2019-11-17T08:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:16:49.000Z","uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec94f5e0cfe408465b1eeaabe72607e9ebf6dd8","tid":1729444,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"1.要出TG<br />\n2.要出水炮車<br />\n3.水炮車要射藍色水<br />\n4.要有畜聾<br />\n5.畜聾最少要30隻<br />\n6.示威者不能防守反擊，要全隊都攻出來<br />\n7.示威者不能壓迫式防守，要給防暴對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.示威者不能擺RB<br />\n9.要出海綿彈，橡膠子彈<br />\n10.至少要開一槍實彈<br />\n11.示威者不能反擊POPO<br />\n12.至少要有飛虎<br />\n13.飛虎要裝備AR-15<br />\n14.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使POPO徹退了，3毛也會說POPO出力，說示威者是靠運氣，說有高人背後制止。3毛是可以找到一條理由來說明POPO未出力。"},{"pid":"e254952f6b2f06818d723b3adf6303f539337fde","tid":1729444,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"甴種狗得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e378974f05fe49a1e4d5813a688e135fc335df","tid":1729444,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaaea00ccb0c9d76381a4873369145886e07ddb","tid":1729444,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}